-= Kitchen =-

As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you make out a sliced red hot pepper, a red onion, a raw purple potato, a red apple, a black pepper and a knife. You can see a stove. Why don't you take a picture of it, it'll last longer! The stove is conventional. The stove appears to be empty.

There is an open frosted-glass door leading south. There is an exit to the west.

-= Kitchen =-

As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you make out a sliced red hot pepper, a red onion, a raw purple potato, a red apple, a black pepper and a knife. You can see a stove. Why don't you take a picture of it, it'll last longer! The stove is conventional. The stove appears to be empty.

There is an open frosted-glass door leading south. There is an exit to the west.

-= Kitchen =-

As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you make out a sliced red hot pepper, a red onion, a raw purple potato, a red apple, a black pepper and a knife. You can see a stove. Why don't you take a picture of it, it'll last longer! The stove is conventional. The stove appears to be empty.

There is an open frosted-glass door leading south. There is an exit to the west.
